snippet.title: Star Fox NES Playthrough
snippet.description:
An old fan game I did back in August of 2008, over the period of about two weeks with the help of two friends (Mario Panighetti and Serguey Parkhomovsky). It's not a lot, but I'm proud of the results. 

Fake Geocities-like download page over here: http://www.galigogames.com/sfnes/
